Learning Rate Scheduler Modülleri

Farklı scheduling stratejileri:
1. Cosine Annealing - Smooth decay
2. Linear Warmup + Decay - Stabil
3. Polynomial Decay - Power-based
4. Constant + Warmup - Basit ama etkili

