python scripts/train.py --config configs/tiny.yaml

# Multi-GPU
torchrun --nproc_per_node=4 scripts/train.py --config 
configs/small.yaml
```

## Mimari

```
Layer 0-3:   Mamba Blocks (SSM)     → Local, fast
Layer 4-5:   Gated Attention       → Transitional
Layer 6-11:  Flash Attention      → Global reasoning
```

